episodes.title: In 1080p an interview with Jim jones doctor & jesse jackson And others
episodes.description: At 16 mins mark you can here an interview with Jesse Jackson Civil rights activist talking about Jim Jones and people's temple recorded on 20th November 1978 after that their is a interview with Dr. Carlton Goodlett was a physician and psychiatrist who treated Jim Jones and other Peoples Temple members in California from 1971 to 1976 and had kept in contact with Jones after that other interviews about people's temple and Jonestown

episodes.title: 90 MIns of 1080p footage of Jonestown aftermath mass grave, interviews,press conference
episodes.description: 1 hour and 30 minutes of 1080p unedited raw footage of Jonestown aftermath showing the mass grave being dug, interviews,press conference, coffins at church and other things including the auction of the victims belongings the video was recorded in November/December 1978

episodes.title: In 1080p Interviews with people who were involved defected or have family members in People's Temple
episodes.description: In 1080p various Interviews with people who were involved with people temple unedited footage recorded in November or December 1978

episodes.title: Unedited footage of outside people's temple and other clips in 1080p
episodes.description: high quality stock footage of people's temple after Jonestown deaths in November/December 1978

episodes.title: In 1080p the coffins and gravesite of the Jonestown victims & interviews
episodes.description: At the end of the  video you can see In 1080p the coffins and gravesite of the Jonestown victims also interviews with Congressman Peter McCloskey about Jonestown mass suicide. A interview of two former Peoples’ Temple adherents unedited.

episodes.title: In 1080p 45 mins of raw unedited video footage the day after Jonestown mass suicide
episodes.description:
45 mins of raw unedited video footage the day after Jonestown mass suicide graphic at the end 
 includes many shots of  Gurvich also seen inside the helicopter crying after seeing the bodies plus other interviews unedited

episodes.title: interview with a friend and the father of Jenn Gurvich a member of the Jim Jones religious group
episodes.description:
This video is a interview with a friend and the father of Jenn Gurvich who was a member of the Jim Jones religious group in 1080p
 Graphic video in high quality of the dead bodies lay about Jonestown at the end of the video
